snippet.title: CONFIRMED? - Amber Heard NOT FIRED from Aquaman 2 as Mera?
snippet.description:
CONFIRMED? - Amber Heard NOT FIRED from Aquaman 2 as Mera?

Scooper Mikey Sutton claims that WB's sticking by Amber Heard by keeping her in Aquaman 2 despite the controversy surrounding her and intense online backlash.

If true, it would fall in line with WB's recent behavior regarding its stars. The studio seems resistant to cancel culture and often sticks by its talent when drama arises. 

After all, they didn't fire Ezra Miller or Johnny Depp, and they haven't fired Joss Whedon or Geoff Johns from other studio projects either, at least not as of now.

I discuss in this video, so check it out.
